  <p class = "padded">
  Welcome to <%= CONFIG[:name] %>! <%= CONFIG[:name] %> is for commissioners and commission artists. It provides a place to connect, tools to streamline the commission process for both sides, and the opportunity to display the work you do and the work that's been done for you. You can search for artists by tags (the kind of artwork they do) and by commission statuses (open, closed, etc.). If you're an artist, you can be searched by potential commissioners in the same way.
  </p>

  <p class = "spaced">
  Some things you can do once you've registered:
  <p>

  <ul>
    <li>Set up your profile: set an avatar and fill out the information about you you want displayed on the main page.</li>
