    <li>Upload picture submissions to your gallery or other pools.</li>
    <li>Comment on submissions and send PMs.</li>
    <li>Use our built-in <%= link_to "kanban workboard", "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kanban_board" %> as an intelligent commission queue.</li>
    <li>Make custom order forms that you as an artist can send to those who want to order work from you.</li>
    <li>Order work from open artists.</li>
  </ul>

  <p>
